{"tid":1857374,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳馮富珍稱世衛讚賞中國努力 哽咽籲艱難時候團結一致","createTime":"2020-02-02T07:05:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-02T19:40:22.000Z","uid":10338,"like":2,"dislike":63,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"879e122804b7fc56b873a184c1fd9adc13869db6","tid":1857374,"uid":10338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T07:05:13.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】世界衛生組織前總幹事陳馮富珍接受內地中央廣播電視台專訪，陳馮富珍表示，世衛讚賞中國政府在疫情公開以及防控疫情方面所做的努力，表示防控疫情的發展需要全球協作與努力。<br />\n<br />\n陳馮富珍一度聲音哽咽，稱醫護人員已經很辛苦了，向防治新型冠狀病毒肺炎疫情的一線醫務人員表示敬意，也要保護自己，國家肯定盡所能提供物質。陳馮富珍呼籲，在艱難時候團結一致、眾志成城，要相信國家，一定能打贏病毒。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1NZKPwm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1NZKPwm.jpg&h=61113df9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d69c3d717766fe9785f1f440c9ce033815df4985","tid":1857374,"uid":8014,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T07:06:49.000Z","msg":"連支那人都唔信<br />\n<br />\n都仲敢講出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df77d6e3f669d02e3e0a1bc4ed171338330d5043","tid":1857374,"uid":149844,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T07:08:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9pwJkD2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9pwJkD2.png&h=9ef3ab2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n解體了"},{"pid":"d24bfa920fa0f3d98ce125318cfb41f017a3eefb","tid":1857374,"uid":155095,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T07:09:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/chicken-25_9mIgn_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fchicken-25_9mIgn_1200x0.png&h=76dbdda8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/1815000/1818326/chan_fung_thumb_20170522_c_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2F